item.description:
I have 2 tee times on Sunday, July 10th at 1:10pm and 1:20pm at Black Swan Country Club in Georgetown. Greens Fee is $67 and includes cart. Easy to get to off Rte. 95.

Has a driving range and nice club house for those who like to gather post round. This used to be a private club, previously known as The Georgetown Country Club. I think it is now one of the better public golfing values/venues on the north shore. Join if you can.

Also, please bring $1 to help Amy cover the costs of this year's Meetup license. Thanks!

http://golf.blackswancountryclub.com/index.html
